</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[264,1323,404,470]" box="[312,1323,444,470]" pageId="2" pageNumber="27">
The generic name refers to the short body (
<emphasis box="[812,871,444,469]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="27">brevi</emphasis>
: short; 
<emphasis box="[959,1020,444,469]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="27">soma</emphasis>
: body). Gender feminine.
</paragraph>
